# рџ“– Overview

Project Sentinel is an enterprise-grade incremental data ingestion pipeline built using **Databricks Auto Loader**, **PySpark**, and **Delta Lake** following the **BronzeвЂ“SilverвЂ“Gold Medallion Architecture**.

The pipeline automatically detects newly arrived transaction files, ingests only new data using checkpointing, transforms raw data into clean and trusted datasets, and generates business-ready analytical insights.

The project demonstrates several production-oriented Data Engineering concepts including:

- Incremental Data Ingestion
- Databricks Auto Loader
- Delta Lake
- Medallion Architecture
- Schema Enforcement
- Schema Evolution
- Late Data Handling
- Structured Streaming
- Data Validation
- Deduplication
- Pipeline Monitoring
- Pipeline Logging
- Failure Handling
- Rule-based Anomaly Detection
- Automated Email Notifications
- SQL Analytics

---

# рџЋЇ Project Objectives

- Build an incremental data ingestion pipeline.
- Implement the BronzeвЂ“SilverвЂ“Gold Medallion Architecture.
- Demonstrate Schema Enforcement and Schema Evolution.
- Handle late-arriving data.
- Clean, validate and deduplicate transactional data.
- Generate business-ready Gold layer datasets.
- Monitor pipeline execution.
- Maintain execution logs.
- Detect anomalous transactions.
- Automatically notify users after pipeline execution.
- Simulate a production-ready Data Engineering workflow.

